Purpose
- Monitor the Regulations control model as a live governance system, not as a documentation artifact.
- Detect allow-list bypass, identity loss, audit failures, monitoring blind spots, and misleading health states before they become compliance incidents.
- Produce actionable alerts with exact evidence, exact thresholds, and a next operator action.

Mission
- Watch the horizontal Regulations runtime end to end across gateway, PAL, monitoring, analytics, governance API, and compliance UI surfaces.
- Distinguish real governance from partial, stale, in-memory, or training-branded approximations.
- Escalate control failures early enough that unhealthy or unauditable actions cannot be treated as compliant.

